title.rendered: WESTERN FILTERS Nissan Navara 2015-on 2.3L ST NP300 4×4 YS23 DOHC Di 16V – Fuel Manager Pre Filter Water Separator Dual Bracket Kit OS-17-FM

content.rendered:
Fuel Manager Pre Filter/Water Separator Kit
Nissan Navara 2.3L ST NP300 (2015 on)
D23 YS23 DOHC Di 16V

** DOES NOT INCLUDE BRACKET!!
** For Companion Provent Bracket Kit: OS-PROV-17B

This kit fits directly onto our Provent Catch Can kit using the same bracket, utilising one bracket for two very important uses and protecting your vehicle ! Fuel Manager is a unique, patented, modular diesel fuel filter/water separator system that can be customized for virtually any application. Each employ unique fiLation process, trapping more impurities and water without impeding the flow rate. The product’s design permits the replacement of elements without the use of tools and without spilling fuel, making service easy in the shop or in the field. When an element is replaced, an easily opened drain valve allows the filter to be completely and neatly emptied before it is removed.

Download Provent PDF Installation Instructions >

View Installation Guide >
